{"tid":1438302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祖國出手了 Britain calls for independent investigation in HK","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:39:36.000Z","uid":108201,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b38d1f7cebe267c396db404496c4ae6aa2ec4475","tid":1438302,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:01.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我哋等左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-britain/britain-calls-for-independent-investigation-into-hong-kong-protests-idUSKCN1UZ223?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Reuters%2FworldNews+%28Reuters+World+News%29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-britain%2Fbritain-calls-for-independent-investigation-into-hong-kong-protests-idUSKCN1UZ223%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DworldNews%26utm_source%3Dfeedburner%26utm_medium%3Dfeed%26utm_campaign%3DFeed%253A%2BReuters%252FworldNews%2B%2528Reuters%2BWorld%2BNews%2529&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=56e14929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-britain%2Fbritain-calls-for-independent-investigation-into-hong-kong-protests-idUSKCN1UZ223%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DworldNews%26utm_source%3Dfeedburner%26utm_medium%3Dfeed%26utm_campaign%3DFeed%253A%2BReuters%252FworldNews%2B%2528Reuters%2BWorld%2BNews%2529&h=fec739d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-britain/britain-calls-for-independent-investigation-into-hong-kong-protests-idUSKCN1UZ223?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Reuters%2FworldNews+%28Reuters+World+News%29</a><br />\n<br />\nLONDON (Reuters) - British foreign minister Dominic Raab called on Friday for an independent investigation into the recent protests in its former colony Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nIn a phone call with Hong Kong chief executive Carrie Lam, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Raab condemned the violence but emphasized the right to peaceful protest.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The Foreign Secretary emphasized the need to find a way forward through meaningful political dialogue, and a fully independent investigation into recent events as a way to build trust,&rdquo; the Foreign Office in London said in a statement.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;(He) condemned violent acts by all sides but emphasized the right to peaceful protest, noting that hundreds of thousands of Hong Kong people had chosen this route to express their views,&rdquo; it added.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;He underlined that the violence should not cloud the lawful actions of the majority.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n口交部聽日點回應？好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955338884c12b239b8d5e8abfb48a50eb373cbf","tid":1438302,"uid":55956,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:34:50.000Z","msg":"說三道四 1賠1千"},{"pid":"08f41d282912800fdea5b4fff939adec8f38272e","tid":1438302,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4955338884c12b239b8d5e8abfb48a50eb373cbf","tid":1438302,"uid":55956,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:34:50.000Z","msg":"說三道四 1賠1千"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"用心險惡 1賠1"},{"pid":"d87c46b26a94bdc23ef74835e97851543d07e390","tid":1438302,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b421eabca6480938e48ab72138fe9eeaff7e3ce2","tid":1438302,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"rep